<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,474,681]" pageId="4" pageNumber="367">Integument lustrous black. Body dorsally subglabrous, ventrally with some whitish hairs on center of metasternum. Spots formed by golden and light green scales. Eyes, antennae and tarsomeres black.</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5098854" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5098854" box="[151,1348,1846,1870]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5098854/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="367" startId="4.[151,250,1846,1870]" targetBox="[151,1435,704,1822]" targetPageId="4">
